{"type": "article", "id": 26866, "title": "显示器拓展夹", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123736UIBdRo21n8xtE5wr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>平板设备现在也可以变身为第二块屏幕了。为了更好地利用这些产品，<a href=\"http://www.oscar-diaz.net/\">Oscar Diaz Studio</a> 设计了这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pixoproducts/pixo-magnetic-tablet-mount-for-desktop-computers\">PIXO</a> 的显示器拓展夹，适用于所有重量在 750 克以下、厚度不超过 9 毫米的平板设备。对于那些需要预览平板上效果的开发者来说，在同一视线水平上完成操作方便得多了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123732SDiFzCyaTjIKecGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123732KBE8vwoiU9LO2tSf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62794118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123733Dq7Urv56fH2S9hzM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123733RA8MpgosZDfz1at0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}